     Index
       0   → null
       1   → (A,10) → (Q,40)
       2   → null
       3   → (B,20)
       4   → null
       5   → (C,30)
       ...
       15  → null
       
   Important Internal Properties
   --------------------------------------------
   | Property         | Default Value          |
   | ---------------- | ---------------------- |
   | Initial capacity | 16                     |
   | Load factor      | 0.75                   |
   | Resize threshold | capacity × load factor |
   
   Ex: 16 × 0.75 = 12
   
   When size becomes 12 → HashMap resizes.
     Old capacity: 16
     New capacity: 32
     
   
